{"tid":1768717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳波波為支援企業和就業措施見傳媒","createTime":"2019-12-04T09:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T09:32:52.000Z","uid":307270,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5d57320c8dd2aa4da96b7d8b01a6870a283d0a26","tid":1768717,"uid":307270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:15:15.000Z","msg":"稅就有份交 糖就無份食 仲話我搞亂個經濟變赤字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1) 非住宅用戶75%的水費及排污費，上限水費20,000元，排污費12,500元。政府收入減少3.5億元，25萬個非住宅用戶受惠。<br />\n2) 為每位合資格的非住宅用戶提供75%的電費補貼，上限5,000元，為期四個月， 等候立法會撥款後開始，料惠及43萬戶。<br />\n3) 非住宅物業，進一步差餉寬免，提高至5,000元。<br />\n2018/19課稅年度，利得稅、薪捧稅、個人入息課稅納稅人，可以申請分期繳付稅項。若得到稅務局批准，會豁免未繳交稅款的附加稅，為期不超過一年。<br />\n4) 啟德郵輪碼頭租金減免，105艘船與6個商戶受惠。<br />\n5) 回收企業提供一次性租金津貼，500間街角回收店、400個露天回收場受惠。<br />\n6) 僱員再培訓局「特別愛增值」，提高津貼額從4000元增至5800元。涉及3.5億元開支。<br />\n優化「展翅青年計劃」，惠及600年輕人。<br />\nTotal 總金額超過40億元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/live/?v=738932469944580&not;if_id=1575448110283013&not;if_t=live_video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2Flive%2F%3Fv%3D738932469944580%C2%ACif_id%3D1575448110283013%C2%ACif_t%3Dlive_video&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDQFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=b49f45ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/live/?v=738932469944580&not;if_id=1575448110283013&not;if_t=live_video</a><br />\n(Source: Economic Digest)"},{"pid":"2034d8e8fdb5dab81bd7ff502f13a7ecb57a5401","tid":1768717,"uid":322732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"乜啟德仲有商戶架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼城一樣"},{"pid":"e2cf196189679c2ba1ada3124806c6f2eac4b405","tid":1768717,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:28:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},